{
  "stem": "23155.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it doesn't take me long to pick up a language.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't really dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived from day to day, even at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't make really much difference to me because it was-- it was-- it was a very hard time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even if I would have gone to a small town, leaving home, living with relatives who had to put up with me, it wasn't something they really looked forward to.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were already-- at that time I thought they were old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they weren't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But here they had a grown up daughter who was married.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here I was, and there were certain laws that I had to be home at 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time I already joined a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had meetings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And perhaps I like to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was 5:00 to 8:00, and I had to be home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I started running like crazy to be home on time that nobody should catch me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would arrive at my, my aunt's apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course it was my poor uncle opened the door, and he had to be nasty to me because she told him that I shouldn't be late and that I put them in jeopardy because I live with them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you know, you have to be home at 8:00, and they could have caught me and who knows what.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was an-- it was very unsettling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called El Al.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it wasn't-- it was like the Social Democrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't too much to the left, and it wasn't too much to the right.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The El Al people, when they went to Israel, they lived on a kibbutz, but not like Hashomer Hatzair, where you really didn't own anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
